{"tid":1532423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[港版還願]21歲女被謀殺 4人被捕包括父母及法師","createTime":"2019-09-02T13:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:19:19.000Z","uid":3302,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1644a39396bb2e6bed221155978ea95df2c80352","tid":1532423,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190902/mobile/bkn-20190902115954085-0902_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190902%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190902115954085-0902_00822_001.html&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ajKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=ad0f477f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190902/mobile/bkn-20190902115954085-0902_00822_001.html</a><br />\n西貢21歲女遭謀殺伏屍村屋 4人被捕包括父母及法師<br />\n<br />\n西貢發生命案。現場是龍尾村一幢3層高村屋，上址窗戶及門口貼有多張「道靈符」。今日（2日）早上7時許，警方接獲報案，指一名21歲女子昏迷倒臥於村屋上層位置內。警方及救護員接報到場，經檢驗後，證實女事主已經死亡。<br />\n據悉，由於死者身上有多處瘀傷，警方懷疑事件另有內情，隨即封鎖現場一帶調查，並於附近草叢作地氈式搜索。警方調查後，相信事件有可疑，至晚上7時許，2男2女黑布蒙頭由警員押走，警員檢走一批證物，包括以紅筆寫有「惡魔」字眼的袋、棉被及一個疑似鐵剷。警方目前正作進一步調查，案件列作謀殺，交由黃大仙警區反黑組跟進。<br />\n據了解，死者天生患有智障，與父母同住上址。約一年前，父母在「睇風水」時，結識了一名自稱為法師的男子，對方聲稱能協助轉運，雙方關係愈趨緊密，該名法師及一名聲稱是其契女的女子，其後更遷進村屋居住。今早母親起床時發現女兒不省人事，揭發命案。據悉，警方懷疑事主生前長期遭受不恰當對待，以及曾遭硬物襲擊頭部。而事主父母則聲稱並無落手殺人。"},{"pid":"c8bd6d4f20d330b950a6357ebac5471453033cbc","tid":1532423,"uid":244044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"要聲討依對父母，咁樣對自己小朋友"},{"pid":"6db397d9bbe0760dbaaa8b23062626b37106e125","tid":1532423,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"習近平小熊維尼呢嘛叭唭<br />\n陸恭銘"},{"pid":"f71ce61a49c93629f0fa2ce86fb4d7da5109f016","tid":1532423,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8bd6d4f20d330b950a6357ebac5471453033cbc","tid":1532423,"uid":244044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"要聲討依對父母，咁樣對自己小朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:43:52.000Z","msg":"有人懷疑黑警嫁媧"},{"pid":"21d847007fcb028287ff6e9cca1e36fb1d1d3f16","tid":1532423,"uid":4645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:45:09.000Z","msg":"硬物襲擊頭部 會唔會係警棍"},{"pid":"e671a4297a4f2b1c5ff6ba7d155083e3f8ecb752","tid":1532423,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins>香港人一定要知！</ins></strong></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"928a94f89e77796d86085857e5a778efed9a112b","tid":1532423,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"而事主父母則聲稱<span style=\"color: red;\">並無落手</span>殺人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5c58305b4f3274c789d5a37e86cd953b18f012","tid":1532423,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"睇嚟對父母先係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h